<div class="pop-up-modal sr-info-modal" id="modal-product-usp-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby=">{{ pages.shipping-returns.title }}" aria-describedby="Learn more about Shipping and Returns">
  <div tabindex="0" class="pop-up-content">
    <span tabindex="0" class="close-button" id="modal-product-usp-1__close">&times;</span>
    <h4 class="pop-up-modal__title">Super-fast just got faster with same-day delivery.</h4>
    <div class="pop-up-modal__body">
      <p>
        We are pleased to offer same-day delivery when orders are placed before 8am EST within the Greater Toronto Area*. Orders over $69+ enjoy the added benefit of FREE same-day delivery. At check-out, delivery availability and options will appear where available (<a target="_blank" href="https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/viewer?mid=1KJBqxC5YSFMYRC4KjkvY4xb66DlHPz-o&ll=43.61711251532798%2C-79.36620245000002&z=9">service map</a>). Any orders that are placed after 8am EST will arrive the next day. 
      </p>
      <p>
        <small>* In cases where package dimensions and weight are exceptional; orders will be shipped ground. </small>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

