    <span tabindex="0" class="close-button" id="modal-product-usp-2__close">&times;</span>
    <h4 class="pop-up-modal__title">Enjoy the convenience of Express Shipping!</h4>
    <div class="pop-up-modal__body">
      <p>
        Express shipping is a premium service available to all orders. <strong>Orders over $69+ enjoy the added benefit of FREE express shipping*.</strong>
      </p>
      <p>
        <small>* In cases where package dimensions, weight or remoteness of delivery address are exceptional; orders will be shipped by ground. </small>
      </p>
      
      <img src="{{ 'c6_standard-express-shipping-updated.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="express shipping map">
      
      <h5>The following is a province breakdown of delivery times:</h5>
      <ul>
        <li>AB, BC, ON, QC: 1-2 business days</li>
        <li>MB, NB, NL, NS, PE, SK: 1-3 business days</li>
        <li>NT, YT, NU: 3-5 business days</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

